section.def:
Registrar (登記官) means
            the Registrar of Marriages under the principal Ordinance and includes a deputy
            registrar;

paragraph.content:
rules, forms and fees for any application by an officiating minister for the
                Registrar’s consent under section 7 and for information under
                    section 9;

for further cases in which an officiating minister should be relieved from
                penalties notwithstanding that he has been unable to give any certificate under
                    section 7;
